^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now clearly on this hand I will bid 4@S. But first let me discuss the bidding if the auction went as follows: 1N-P-2@C-P-2@D-P-?. Absent any conventional agreement, I would bid 3@S. That would show a game forcing hand asking partner to bid 4@S with 3-card support and 3N otherwise.|sk||mb|4S|
