^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|First let me mention that my recommended bidding is 4@H-P-P-P. But I like to comment on the defense. The defense by East West was very good. After  cashing 2 hearts, East's 3rd heart was high. When giving partner a ruff, the size of the spot you play is a suit preference signal. |
